"1 1/2 cups fat-free milk","1 1/2 cups water","  Cooking spray","2  Gala apples, peeled and cut into 1/2-inch cubes (about 3 cups)","1 cup uncooked steel-cut oats","2 tablespoons brown sugar","1 1/2 tablespoons butter, softened","1/4 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 cup maple syrup","2 tablespoons hazelnuts, chopped"